1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 27=

3
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:50,120
(Six years later)

4
00:00:52,180 --> 00:00:54,619
Is everything ready
for taking over the house?

5
00:00:54,620 --> 00:00:55,700
Everything's ready.

6
00:00:56,300 --> 00:00:57,180
Go ahead.

7
00:01:03,820 --> 00:01:05,780
Uncle, this is my ball.

8
00:01:07,020 --> 00:01:07,620
Here.

9
00:01:07,900 --> 00:01:08,980
Thank you, uncle.

10
00:01:10,340 --> 00:01:12,100
Why are you playing here
alone at the hospital?

11
00:01:12,460 --> 00:01:13,619
I'm used to it.

12
00:01:13,620 --> 00:01:15,259
I've been in the hospital
since I was little.

13
00:01:15,260 --> 00:01:17,220
Everyone here knows me.

14
00:01:17,900 --> 00:01:19,419
(If we had a child,)

15
00:01:19,420 --> 00:01:21,100
(they'd probably be about this age too.)

16
00:01:24,740 --> 00:01:25,740
That's impressive.

17
00:01:27,060 --> 00:01:28,020
How old are you?

18
00:01:28,140 --> 00:01:30,020
I was born in the Year of Bingchen.

19
00:01:30,700 --> 00:01:31,940
The Year of Bingchen?

20
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:34,299
So you're five years old?

21
00:01:34,300 --> 00:01:35,099
That's right.

22
00:01:35,100 --> 00:01:36,100
Xiaoxiao.

23
00:01:36,340 --> 00:01:37,180
Xiaoxiao!

24
00:01:39,180 --> 00:01:40,020
Xiaoxiao!

25
00:01:40,300 --> 00:01:41,420
Mom!

26
00:01:41,820 --> 00:01:43,180
Where did you run off to?

27
00:01:43,260 --> 00:01:43,859
Mom,

28
00:01:43,860 --> 00:01:45,939
there was a really
handsome uncle just now.

29
00:01:45,940 --> 00:01:47,419
We were chatting.

30
00:01:47,420 --> 00:01:48,300
Uncle?

31
00:01:48,340 --> 00:01:48,940
Mm.

32
00:01:57,760 --> 00:02:02,800
♪Love quietly hides within the wind♪

33
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:08,680
♪Falling into your smile before my eyes♪

34
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:15,960
♪Stirring my dreams
and awakening my heart♪

35
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:20,440
♪Past and future both fade away♪

36
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:27,000
♪Love is so strange,
the way it entangles me♪

37
00:02:28,100 --> 00:02:28,900
Shaoyuan.

38
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:37,199
♪Still gently holding onto the♪

39
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:41,600
♪Happy game that began within a dream♪

40
00:02:41,900 --> 00:02:45,240
♪Joy and pleasure♪

41
00:02:47,620 --> 00:02:48,300
Are you alright?

42
00:02:48,980 --> 00:02:49,740
I'm fine.

43
00:02:49,820 --> 00:02:51,260
Just scraped my skin a little.

44
00:02:53,100 --> 00:02:53,740
Let's go.

45
00:02:54,100 --> 00:02:54,740
Mm.

46
00:02:57,160 --> 00:03:02,639
♪Forcing me to trade pain for the past♪

47
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:06,040
♪In this world♪

48
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:26,520
♪Love is a beautiful exchange♪

49
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:32,560
♪Hearts connecting in that very moment♪

50
00:03:37,460 --> 00:03:39,259
(Seeing you're still alive)

51
00:03:39,260 --> 00:03:40,780
(is enough for me.)

52
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:42,660
(Of the two of us,)

53
00:03:42,900 --> 00:03:44,980
(at least one should live happily.)

54
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:50,800
♪Love is so strange,
the way it entangles me♪

55
00:03:59,820 --> 00:04:00,940
Where did you hide Xiaoxiao?

56
00:04:01,380 --> 00:04:02,760
We've never registered a marriage,

57
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,520
and we've never
been husband and wife in truth.

58
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:06,080
What right do you have to take her away?

59
00:04:07,180 --> 00:04:08,179
Darling, I heard

60
00:04:08,180 --> 00:04:09,740
you met an old friend today.

61
00:04:11,140 --> 00:04:13,140
Did you think that now he's back,

62
00:04:13,340 --> 00:04:15,060
you and Xiaoxiao would finally be safe?

63
00:04:15,420 --> 00:04:16,500
What do you mean by that?

64
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:20,620
Haven't I suffered enough all these years,
being threatened and tormented by you?

65
00:04:21,500 --> 00:04:23,419
You deliberately
gave Xiaoxiao a false birth year.

66
00:04:23,420 --> 00:04:24,940
What exactly are you trying to do?

67
00:04:27,540 --> 00:04:28,980
What am I trying to do?

68
00:04:29,540 --> 00:04:30,579
For the past six years,

69
00:04:30,580 --> 00:04:33,820
I've given you
and that child a comfortable life.

70
00:04:34,780 --> 00:04:36,940
Yet you wouldn't even let me touch you.

71
00:04:37,460 --> 00:04:39,500
Every single time,
you threatened me with death.

72
00:04:40,060 --> 00:04:42,220
Haven't I treated you well enough?

73
00:04:42,700 --> 00:04:45,180
And yet you're still thinking
about Lu Shaoyuan.

74
00:04:46,820 --> 00:04:47,579
Don't forget,

75
00:04:47,580 --> 00:04:50,180
six years ago, you killed him
with your own hands.

76
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,740
Do you think he could ever forgive you?

77
00:04:53,340 --> 00:04:55,460
You've stayed faithful
to him all these years,

78
00:04:58,700 --> 00:04:59,940
but does he even know that?

79
00:05:01,740 --> 00:05:03,500
What he sees

80
00:05:03,820 --> 00:05:06,540
is six years of you sharing my bed.

81
00:05:10,540 --> 00:05:11,620
Oh, right.

82
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:13,500
Let me remind you of something.

83
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,539
If he ever finds out that this child

84
00:05:15,540 --> 00:05:17,100
is his biological daughter,

85
00:05:18,140 --> 00:05:19,260
then that child's life

86
00:05:19,860 --> 00:05:21,259
will be in danger too.

87
00:05:21,260 --> 00:05:23,340
Gu Shaoyan, you're insane!

88
00:05:25,460 --> 00:05:27,060
What, still want to kill me?

89
00:05:28,060 --> 00:05:29,740
Too bad you can't.

90
00:05:30,340 --> 00:05:31,700
If I die,

91
00:05:31,740 --> 00:05:33,940
Xiaoxiao will be buried with me too.

92
00:06:01,660 --> 00:06:02,900
Lu Shaoyuan!

93
00:06:11,260 --> 00:06:11,940
Guards.

94
00:06:12,620 --> 00:06:13,340
Take him away.

95
00:06:14,260 --> 00:06:15,140
What are you doing?

96
00:06:15,660 --> 00:06:16,580
What are you doing?

97
00:06:17,140 --> 00:06:18,140
Lu Shaoyuan,

98
00:06:18,260 --> 00:06:19,740
even if you're the Commander in Chief,

99
00:06:20,300 --> 00:06:22,980
you can't just arrest
a city commander on a whim.

100
00:06:30,020 --> 00:06:31,420
Cheng Yi, Commander of Yancheng,

101
00:06:31,820 --> 00:06:32,900
for smuggling opium

102
00:06:32,900 --> 00:06:34,400
(Arrest Warrant)
and violating the opium ban,

103
00:06:35,140 --> 00:06:36,400
you're hereby placed under arrest.

104
00:06:40,780 --> 00:06:41,900
Your house,

105
00:06:43,660 --> 00:06:44,700
your woman,

106
00:06:46,140 --> 00:06:47,020
I'll take them all.

107
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:49,980
Madam,

108
00:06:50,900 --> 00:06:51,579
he's trying

109
00:06:51,580 --> 00:06:53,700
to destroy this family

110
00:06:54,220 --> 00:06:56,180
and tear us apart.

111
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:00,660
You can't arrest him.

112
00:07:00,900 --> 00:07:01,900
You can't arrest him.

113
00:07:11,660 --> 00:07:12,499
He endangered Yancheng

114
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:13,580
and harmed the people.

115
00:07:14,020 --> 00:07:15,260
Why shouldn't he be arrested?

116
00:07:18,820 --> 00:07:20,420
No matter how many wrongs he's done,

117
00:07:20,460 --> 00:07:22,360
you still can't take the law
into your own hands.

118
00:07:22,700 --> 00:07:24,060
You can't ignore the law.

119
00:07:25,180 --> 00:07:26,020
Darling,

120
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:28,300
don't beg him.

121
00:07:29,540 --> 00:07:31,940
I've failed you and the child.

122
00:07:33,060 --> 00:07:35,020
I've failed both of you.

123
00:07:39,580 --> 00:07:41,540
Wasn't Miss Zhuang
talking to me about the law?

124
00:07:42,700 --> 00:07:43,980
Then let me tell you this.

125
00:07:47,300 --> 00:07:48,900
In Yancheng, I am the law.

126
00:07:49,460 --> 00:07:50,340
Take him away!

127
00:07:51,220 --> 00:07:52,020
Lu Shaoyuan!

128
00:07:55,980 --> 00:07:56,859
I'm begging you.

129
00:07:56,860 --> 00:07:57,739
You can't arrest him.

130
00:07:57,740 --> 00:07:58,499
Please let him go.

131
00:07:58,500 --> 00:07:59,299
I'm begging you.

132
00:07:59,300 --> 00:08:00,260
I'm begging you!

133
00:08:08,140 --> 00:08:09,100
Please listen to me.

134
00:08:09,260 --> 00:08:10,220
I'm begging you.

135
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:17,280
If someone has to be locked up,
then lock me up instead.

136
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:19,060
Please let him go.

137
00:08:19,260 --> 00:08:20,420
I'm begging you!

138
00:08:23,580 --> 00:08:25,660
If you're going to beg,
then beg properly.

139
00:08:26,380 --> 00:08:27,740
The way Miss Zhuang is acting now

140
00:08:29,100 --> 00:08:30,740
sounds more like a threat.

141
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:40,800
♪Love quietly hides within the wind♪

142
00:08:40,860 --> 00:08:41,639
I'm begging you.

143
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:46,600
♪Falling into your smile before my eyes♪

144
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:51,820
So anyone who breaks the law

145
00:08:52,220 --> 00:08:54,020
can just kneel before me

146
00:08:54,260 --> 00:08:56,220
and have everything forgiven?

147
00:08:56,780 --> 00:08:58,100
Then I'll kneel here

148
00:08:58,140 --> 00:08:59,860
until you're satisfied. Is that enough?

149
00:09:00,580 --> 00:09:01,300
Fine.

150
00:09:02,780 --> 00:09:04,420
Then kneel properly, Miss Zhuang.

151
00:09:04,980 --> 00:09:07,620
Right now, I don't see
any sincerity at all.

152
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:15,200
♪Still gently holding onto the♪

153
00:09:15,500 --> 00:09:16,540
Good.

154
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:19,140
Stay like that.

155
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:23,360
♪Joy and pleasure♪

156
00:09:26,700 --> 00:09:28,540
(Every moment that passes)

157
00:09:28,740 --> 00:09:30,580
(will puts Xiaoxiao in greater danger.)

158
00:09:35,420 --> 00:09:40,559
♪Forcing me to trade pain for the past♪

159
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:44,080
♪In this world♪

160
00:09:44,660 --> 00:09:45,700
Commander-in-Chief,

161
00:09:47,460 --> 00:09:49,420
I really don't have much time left.

162
00:09:49,460 --> 00:09:51,420
I'm begging you, let him go first.

163
00:09:51,540 --> 00:09:53,340
Just let him go.

164
00:09:53,540 --> 00:09:55,099
I'll do whatever you ask.

165
00:09:55,100 --> 00:09:55,940
Alright?

166
00:09:56,180 --> 00:09:58,180
I'm begging you,
please let him go first.

167
00:10:04,380 --> 00:10:05,380
Your clothes are dirty.

168
00:10:08,460 --> 00:10:10,140
Miss Zhuang is dirty too.

169
00:10:10,980 --> 00:10:12,700
Let me help clean you up.

170
00:10:14,380 --> 00:10:15,260
Guards.

171
00:10:16,020 --> 00:10:19,300
Have the Commander personally
prepare bathwater for Madam and me.

172
00:10:30,620 --> 00:10:35,310
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

173
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:41,940
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

174
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:46,020
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

175
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:49,370
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

176
00:10:49,540 --> 00:10:54,660
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

177
00:10:55,780 --> 00:11:00,970
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

178
00:11:02,030 --> 00:11:07,630
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

179
00:11:08,170 --> 00:11:11,550
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

180
00:11:11,800 --> 00:11:14,749
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

181
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:19,889
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

182
00:11:19,890 --> 00:11:24,209
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

183
00:11:24,210 --> 00:11:26,789
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

184
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:29,069
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

185
00:11:29,070 --> 00:11:32,619
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

186
00:11:32,620 --> 00:11:37,149
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

187
00:11:37,150 --> 00:11:39,680
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

188
00:11:39,820 --> 00:11:41,769
♪Still I walk into♪

189
00:11:41,770 --> 00:11:45,369
♪The trap you set without regret♪

190
00:11:45,370 --> 00:11:49,419
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

191
00:11:49,420 --> 00:11:51,999
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

192
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:54,159
♪A stand in can never cross♪

193
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:57,599
♪The shortest distance between us♪

194
00:11:57,600 --> 00:12:02,570
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

195
00:12:02,730 --> 00:12:07,400
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

196
00:12:10,180 --> 00:12:11,749
♪A substitute♪

197
00:12:11,750 --> 00:12:16,750
♪Needs no reason♪

